title: 'News From Babel: Work Resumed On The Tower'  1984
description:
Originally released at 45 rpm for higher quality audio.

Lovely release from 1984, go buy it just for the artwork alone.


Extremely fine psychedelia for the discerning ear.


Saved back in the day when I knew little about bitrate, perhaps.  Although it is a relatively short work, and 128 kbps is tolerable to all but hipsters.


Many have asked, so here it is again, but please seed if you enjoy it and purchase if you are knocked out by it.  Recommended Records catalog some of the greatest music ever laid down.
